2.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo I. Gradante, 2022-06-20\" src=\"ISic001762-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001762_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo I. Gradante, 2022-06-20\" src=\"ISic001762_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001762_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo I. Gradante, 2022-06-20\" src=\"ISic001762_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of autopsy, confirming Orsi</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"4\">4: <span>Orsi: alternatively a similar name like Σωτικός</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>((staurogram)) Here likes Sosimos(?) of beautiful memory</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1893 286 no.34 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
